- IQ2_XXS gate/up wave kernel: /home/noah/repos/ds4/ds4_rocm.c:5337
- Inner table-byte + 8-lane float loop: ds4_rocm.c:5392-5428
- Q2_K down wave kernel: ds4_rocm.c:5451
